（难度水平）相比，很难从面板中脱颖而出。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok7luvf5x2l-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok7luvf5x2l-1024x530.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok7luvf5x2l-1024x530.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok7luvf5x2l-300x155.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok7luvf5x2l-768x397.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.ok7luvf5x2l-jpg.webp 1266w" width="1024" height="530" /></a><br /> （第一个被错过了...）</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.64lrvjfx2lqi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.64lrvjfx2lqi-1024x529.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.64lrvjfx2lqi-1024x529.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.64lrvjfx2lqi-300x155.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.64lrvjfx2lqi-768x397.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.64lrvjfx2lqi-jpg.webp 1269w" width="1024" height="529" /></a><br /> （我不能通过第二个）</p><p> IKE以桌面模式（非VR模式）玩游戏。他用稳定的姿势和一个小的头像作为武器而苦苦挣扎，但是当一个复杂的面板来了时，就有一种无法处理并被吹走的行为。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/7b7cff9f97d92e3d4f188d6262eb8812-kix.cuhu2toptnp1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="htt